{"tid":954890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睡豬圈「人工呼吸救400豬」　27歲正妹年收455萬","createTime":"2018-12-25T03:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T13:36:07.000Z","uid":212399,"like":29,"dislike":102,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"1fc3b4059fbb6c2f53cac0dd28d60d8da3918b4c","tid":954890,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T03:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZnWy1H0qFp9UfQhPF2OwPA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/nownews.hk/acb382954b00a292a29a7f81ca4d8b1a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZnWy1H0qFp9UfQhPF2OwPA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fnownews.hk%2Facb382954b00a292a29a7f81ca4d8b1a&h=94999409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n27歲女生年收455萬元，她全靠養豬！大陸湖南一名27歲女生肖芳接手父親的養豬場，為了照顧6000多頭豬，她每年都搬進豬圈與小豬一起過冬，6年下來更用口對口人工呼吸救活了400多頭豬。而這也讓她年收入高達100多萬元人民幣(超過455萬元台幣)。<br />\n根據陸媒報導，肖芳父親創立煤礦公司，但因為煤炭不景氣，決定在2008年花300多萬元人民幣(逾1364萬元台幣)開養豬場，並在2012年將養豬場交給當時僅21歲的肖芳。其實肖芳從17歲起就在養豬場裡幫忙，也努力學習採精、配種、配藥、接生等專業技術，接手豬圈後，肖芳也開始安排起各項養豬作業。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2205618/org/432b6b25e109f98ba4aa2501a93c98ed.jpg/-zEs-6MHv9Nz80zaZgYEgUDkqO8cI75FOSjn0Tko59E?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2205618%2Forg%2F432b6b25e109f98ba4aa2501a93c98ed.jpg%2F-zEs-6MHv9Nz80zaZgYEgUDkqO8cI75FOSjn0Tko59E%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b133b24e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/jiangsu/crawl/117/w550h367/20181220/oRXe-hqnkypr4719288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fjiangsu%2Fcrawl%2F117%2Fw550h367%2F20181220%2FoRXe-hqnkypr4719288.jpg&h=dfe0a242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肖芳說起養豬工作，由於幫母豬接生困難又需要細心，也沒人要做，因此「協助每月7、80頭母豬生產的工作只有我能幹」，如果小豬在出生時出現「假性窒息」的狀況，她還會親自做人工呼吸，6年來已經救活400多頭小豬；而每年冬天，為了不讓小豬被嚴寒影響，除了把剛出生的小豬放入保溫箱，肖芳也會搬進豬圈和小豬一起生活，一睡就是3個月，直到天氣轉暖才會搬出豬圈。<br />\n「日久生情不僅僅在人與人之間，和動物之間也一樣。」肖芳坦承自己剛接觸養豬時，一度因為他人眼光而覺得自卑，但現在已經全新投入，也發現豬的可愛，甚至將小豬取名為知名卡通粉紅豬主角的「佩奇」。如今才27歲的肖芳已經將養豬場擴大，每年可銷出6000多頭豬，年收達100多萬元人民幣，事業有成，現在唯一的願望就是想遇到真心喜歡的人，願意支持她的事業，收穫一份對的愛情。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.wxrb.com/news/ywtx/201812/W020181220465730423782.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wxrb.com%2Fnews%2Fywtx%2F201812%2FW020181220465730423782.png&h=deeafd82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/1046651\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F1046651&d=HoDbkrHw8ewrkyQVt6SJ5y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=bf4609e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/1046651</a>"},{"pid":"d3676cf270629ee8035878fd60c3b862cd4e9f84","tid":954890,"uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T03:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0decab52434b679082bc930b7855f26fbde780b1","tid":954890,"uid":163797,"like":683,"dislike":3,"score":680,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T03:57:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老味最後張相連隻豬都美顏埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ff527e0e33f36f9997b322fe15dfc804c0c762","tid":954890,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T03:57:14.000Z","msg":"你條女"},{"pid":"17d17394a47d50b7aee484f991dd20c8182b844a","tid":954890,"uid":53672,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"d豬p哂圖咁白淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25003317c55054ebda832b539191351bf4943cdf","tid":954890,"uid":48905,"like":141,"dislike":1,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T03:57:48.000Z","msg":"條女實臭撚到仆街"},{"pid":"3ba25c554f663c41194eb2c4ef2513da9d9cab26","tid":954890,"uid":53672,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"0decab52434b679082bc930b7855f26fbde780b1","tid":954890,"uid":163797,"like":683,"dislike":3,