:13:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZnWy1H0qFp9UfQhPF2OwPA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/nownews.hk/acb382954b00a292a29a7f81ca4d8b1a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZnWy1H0qFp9UfQhPF2OwPA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fnownews.hk%2Facb382954b00a292a29a7f81ca4d8b1a&h=94999409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n27歲女生年收455萬元，她全靠養豬！大陸湖南一名27歲女生肖芳接手父親的養豬場，為了照顧6000多頭豬，她每年都搬進豬圈與小豬一起過冬，6年下來更<span style=\"color: red;\">用口對口</span>人工呼吸救活了400多頭豬。而這也讓她年收入高達100多萬元人民幣(超過455萬元台幣)。<br />\n根據陸媒報導，肖芳父親創立煤礦公司，但因為煤炭不景氣，決定在2008年花300多萬元人民幣(逾1364萬元台幣)開養豬場，並在2012年將養豬場交給當時僅21歲的肖芳。其實肖芳從17歲起就在養豬場裡幫忙，也努力學習<span style=\"color: red;\">採精</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">配種</span>、配藥、接生等專業技術，接手豬圈後，肖芳也開始安排起各項養豬作業。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2205618/org/432b6b25e109f98ba4aa2501a93c98ed.jpg/-zEs-6MHv9Nz80zaZgYEgUDkqO8cI75FOSjn0Tko59E?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2205618%2Forg%2F432b6b25e109f98ba4aa2501a93c98ed.jpg%2F-zEs-6MHv9Nz80zaZgYEgUDkqO8cI75FOSjn0Tko59E%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b133b24e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/jiangsu/crawl/117/w550h367/20181220/oRXe-hqnkypr4719288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fjiangsu%2Fcrawl%2F117%2Fw550h367%2F20181220%2FoRXe-hqnkypr4719288.jpg&h=dfe0a242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肖芳說起養豬工作，由於幫母豬接生困難又需要細心，也沒人要做，因此「協助每月7、80頭母豬生產的工作只有我能幹」，如果小豬在出生時出現「假性窒息」的狀況，她還會親自做人工呼吸，6年來已經救活400多頭小豬；而每年冬天，為了不讓小豬被嚴寒影響，除了把剛出生的小豬放入保溫箱，肖芳也會搬進豬圈和小豬一起生活，一睡就是3個月，直到天氣轉暖才會搬出豬圈。<br />\n「日久生情不僅僅在人與人之間，和動物之間也一樣。」肖芳坦承自己剛接觸養豬時，一度因為他人眼光而覺得自卑，但現在已經全新投入，也發現豬的可愛，甚至將小豬取名為知名卡通粉紅豬主角的「佩奇」。如今才27歲的肖芳已經將養豬場擴大，每年可銷出6000多頭豬，年收達100多萬元人民幣，事業有成，現在唯一的願望就是想遇到真心喜歡的人，願意支持她的事業，收穫一份對的愛情。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.wxrb.com/news/ywtx/201812/W020181220465730423782.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wxrb.com%2Fnews%2Fywtx%2F201812%2FW020181220465730423782.png&h=deeafd82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/1046651\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F1046651&d=HoDbkrHw8ewrkyQVt6SJ5y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=bf4609e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/1046651</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9ad87d249942317f303662b645d727b4cb25059c","tid":954890,"uid":77164,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:24:42.000Z","msg":"賣豬但又愛豬<br />\n咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daca2ec0b2f55fa432daf6c96e7a238d8535c617","tid":954890,"uid":127075,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:26:03.000Z","msg":"殺豬兇手扮愛豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be29a3f156a7afef5e0ee4222d1847441a9cabd9","tid":954890,"uid":145107,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:00:17.000Z","msg":"同啲豬培養感情之後再劏咗佢哋，咁樣仲殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8532919d18c81b979bd5c93db5bced04bbfbff04","tid":954890,"uid":6640,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"我係港豬！我係港豬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快點來吸我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186d635558fc588e64f23523775a078ab453f75e","tid":954890,"uid":133067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"豬閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8388f6656d4f345d94e9e54a978a9a355bbf660","tid":954890,"uid":51620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,